Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全裸巨乳家政妇\NJULIA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要请您多多指教了\N我是JULIA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷，有什么需要的话\N就尽管跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就开始准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您在旁边放松休息就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊，这种天气很适合洗衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有加柔软精洗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以衣服穿起来会又柔软又舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柔软...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很柔软的样子...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家说的不是胸部\N是衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好柔软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还在晒衣服...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你继续晒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样我没办法晒衣服...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服很快就会干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，今天天气很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服会变软吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿起来一定会很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会很舒服啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要晒衣服...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续晒...继续晒...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样我没办法晒衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服好不容易洗的这么柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点太阳要下山了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:13:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变软的是衣服不是胸部啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服比较软啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是胸部是衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多摸几下会变的更软吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不是胸部啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变软了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:14:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有变软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要晒衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不够，还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很美味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去人家会没办法晒衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太阳要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天要黑了啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你要诱惑我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柔软精的香味都没了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天要黑了啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服味道很香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先坐到这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再多尝几下味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样衣服又会脏掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直这样舔胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法去晒完衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等会我还要煮饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你先进去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有衣服要晒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你先回客厅等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在扫浴室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会，不会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以进去洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在在涂沐浴乳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起好多泡沫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在帮你洗身体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的背后很脏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你洗干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.09,0:22:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好软，好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.66,0:22:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你喜欢那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.30,0:22:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在帮你洗前面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.68,0:23:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先把泡沫冲掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一开始先慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.90,0:24:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒好滑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.34,0:24:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在浴缸里面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.45,0:24:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.72,0:24:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒...浴缸好棒...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.73,0:25:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面和里面那边比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.60,0:25:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是里面比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.60,0:25:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.12,0:25:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好滑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.33,0:25:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有洗干净了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.57,0:25:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.64,0:25:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.31,0:25:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人洗澡真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.32,0:25:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.65,0:26:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在帮你洗这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.80,0:26:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.24,0:26:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有洗干净吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.32,0:26:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.23,0:26:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.76,0:26:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样感觉又不一样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.01,0:26:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像被吸进去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.46,0:27:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一脸幸褔的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.65,0:28:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才洗干净的说
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.48,0:28:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了好多出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.52,0:28:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再帮我洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.93,0:28:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你冲干净吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.44,0:29:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.69,0:29:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.56,0:29:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃饺子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.36,0:29:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饺子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.20,0:29:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.20,0:29:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢吃中华料理
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.31,0:29:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.68,0:29:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请再稍等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.79,0:29:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.87,0:30:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.67,0:30:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美味的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.22,0:30:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还有什么想吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.33,0:30:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他想吃的吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.03,0:30:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷，这样很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.57,0:30:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.68,0:30:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.71,0:30:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,油会喷出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.45,0:31:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.46,0:31:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饺子会焦掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.43,0:31:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边的比较重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.00,0:31:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去坐好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.19,0:31:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多拍打几下
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.82,0:31:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用力摇，用力摇
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.66,0:31:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用力摇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.30,0:31:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不够啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.73,0:31:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不够哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.80,0:31:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的很危险啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.14,0:31:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要像地震一样才行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.85,0:32:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再摇快一点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.86,0:32:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.10,0:32:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.71,0:32:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样饺子会焦掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.31,0:32:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好滑
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.95,0:32:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有上油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.08,0:32:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.40,0:32:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面一定很多养份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.77,0:33:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.79,0:33:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东西会焦掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.62,0:33:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还、还不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.87,0:34:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你继续煮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.75,0:34:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.72,0:34:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要像我的肉棒这样才对
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.09,0:34:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.36,0:35:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握住、握住
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.03,0:35:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.08,0:35:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温柔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.79,0:35:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.39,0:35:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.63,0:35:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.57,0:35:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,练习吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.82,0:35:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顶住你的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.31,0:36:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来示范给你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.38,0:36:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转过来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.92,0:36:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.48,0:37:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.83,0:37:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.83,0:37:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还少了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.04,0:37:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.91,0:37:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.32,0:37:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.32,0:37:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始动你的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.30,0:37:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.77,0:38:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样，你学的很快
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.08,0:38:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.05,0:38:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会记下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.87,0:38:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用力夹住
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.85,0:38:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会喷出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.46,0:39:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.74,0:39:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来到这边做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.05,0:39:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.44,0:39:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.16,0:40:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温柔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.60,0:40:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要全部包住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.84,0:40:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.61,0:40:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也从下面来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.62,0:40:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把手往下面移一点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.82,0:40:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后上面用舌头舔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.32,0:41:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面还要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.69,0:41:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.57,0:43:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我学的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.81,0:43:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.96,0:43:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我涂一点油上去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.77,0:45:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.96,0:46:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.43,0:46:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想试吃看看呠道
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.00,0:46:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.14,0:46:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里可以吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.24,0:46:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里是饺子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.95,0:46:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夹住它
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.11,0:46:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.57,0:47:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样做对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.64,0:57:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是美味的饺子...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.26,0:57:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个真棒啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.00,0:57:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像在做梦一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.43,0:57:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后只在电视里看过
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.97,0:57:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想先吃那一道菜
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.44,0:57:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来喂你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.61,0:57:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不挑食嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.18,0:57:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还蛮挑食的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.22,0:57:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.76,0:57:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是被老爷阻碍的饺子
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.37,0:58:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有阻碍你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.01,0:58:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚教到一半就...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.91,0:58:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做的很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.71,0:58:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都粘在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.79,0:58:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.49,0:58:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.09,0:58:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.53,0:58:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.17,0:58:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,油好像太多了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.77,0:58:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是老爷你说油要多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.24,0:58:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.85,0:58:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要吃点心
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.52,0:58:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以帮我准备一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.22,0:58:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃点心
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.46,0:58:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.70,0:59:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,点心
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.37,0:59:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是点心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.43,0:59:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.51,0:59:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.71,1:01:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会用吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.75,1:01:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太懂这个...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.92,1:01:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.52,1:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗，谢谢哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.37,1:01:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这台机器是最新型的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.48,1:02:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要先放柔软的东西上去才能使用
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.91,1:02:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失，失礼了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.25,1:02:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样放上去
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.16,1:02:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样放上去以后
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.66,1:02:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过一会影印机就可以用了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.71,1:02:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心你的头发
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.19,1:02:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是还不够的关系
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.10,1:02:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再帮你弄软一点
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.45,1:03:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经变的更软了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.12,1:03:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.86,1:03:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以用了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.33,1:03:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.04,1:03:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.72,1:03:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要弄软一点吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.65,1:03:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不弄软影印机没办法用
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.66,1:03:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.03,1:03:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.97,1:04:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样会比较快吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.84,1:04:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起会比较快
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.54,1:04:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.05,1:04:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要加一点水才行
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.48,1:04:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水吗...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.95,1:04:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影印机不能碰水吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.43,1:04:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这台是防水的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.23,1:04:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防水吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.36,1:04:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用水以外的东西就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.04,1:04:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你弄更的软哦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.24,1:04:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.76,1:05:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.80,1:05:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光只有一边可能不够
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.70,1:05:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.33,1:05:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以这边也要
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.44,1:05:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.27,1:05:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以印了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.07,1:05:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要再软一点才行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.32,1:06:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢俩位的帮忙哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.56,1:06:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以按住我们的头吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.44,1:07:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等，等等
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.55,1:07:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最懂这台影印机的人
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.45,1:07:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我才对
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.99,1:07:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是让我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.36,1:07:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.56,1:07:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.87,1:08:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是制造这台影印机的公司员工
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.47,1:08:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.91,1:08:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要用影印机的话，得先用某个开关才行
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.09,1:08:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这根开关打开
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.77,1:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两根开关要一起打开才行
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.08,1:08:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让软掉的开关变硬
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.55,1:08:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样才能影印
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.69,1:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以印了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.89,1:08:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要再更硬一点才行
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.10,1:09:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么时间了...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.07,1:09:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你要再快一点才行
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.41,1:09:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还得回家准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.82,1:09:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...这样好了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.09,1:10:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上面涂一点水会比较快吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.56,1:10:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多加一点水上去
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.87,1:10:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得应该是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.04,1:10:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也不太懂啦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.84,1:10:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.35,1:10:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加一点水上去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.02,1:10:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用什么水?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.56,1:10:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你的口水就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.03,1:11:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.20,1:11:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没，没事
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.85,1:12:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多涂一点上去
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.39,1:13:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水分还是不够...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.77,1:14:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边变硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.64,1:14:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用这个来保养一下开关
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.77,1:14:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以用了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.54,1:14:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在把手撑到那边
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.58,1:14:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手撑到那边
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.96,1:15:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后请按着这个开关
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.27,1:15:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，我插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.45,1:15:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该快可以用了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.70,1:15:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.31,1:15:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一会就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.39,1:16:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摇的很厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.85,1:16:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样会更快哦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.86,1:16:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会更快吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.95,1:17:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换别的开关吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.73,1:17:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把脚张开
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.93,1:17:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两根开关都是必需的嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.45,1:19:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么要做的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.29,1:20:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在到柜台那边结账吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.77,1:20:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫店长过来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.01,1:20:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.25,1:20:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要结账吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.02,1:20:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不先结账不能印哦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.15,1:21:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长，她的脚酸了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.19,1:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让她休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.30,1:21:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样会比较轻松吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.71,1:21:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.44,1:22:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快好了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.09,1:22:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.16,1:23:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时，时间...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.60,1:23:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.31,1:23:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还得回去做饭...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.31,1:23:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.61,1:23:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换我这边吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.40,1:25:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了找钱哦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.08,1:25:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长，你还没找零
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.28,1:27:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.49,1:27:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.96,1:30:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来该换我了...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.70,1:30:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.86,1:30:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你印好了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.80,1:30:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢哦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.10,1:30:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.64,1:30:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.27,1:30:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身的肌肉快痛死了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.91,1:30:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.62,1:31:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫老爷你要那么激烈的\N又吸又舔人家的胸部嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.63,1:31:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明记得我不是很激烈啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.00,1:31:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很激烈哦
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.67,1:31:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该没有吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.37,1:31:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想再多吸一点呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.58,1:31:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前要先按摩才行
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.33,1:31:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.92,1:32:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多摩擦下
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.47,1:32:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有这种按摩哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.38,1:32:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.13,1:32:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你开心那就好
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.64,1:33:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手也觉得很僵硬吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.68,1:33:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手也觉得很僵硬吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.78,1:33:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很僵硬哦
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.52,1:33:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你按摩手哦
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.90,1:33:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.93,1:34:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.30,1:34:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力一点
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.31,1:34:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.34,1:34:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.90,1:34:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面也麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.54,1:34:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边也很僵硬
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.71,1:34:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.29,1:35:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.35,1:36:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.90,1:36:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起这样按摩...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.74,1:36:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是这样按比较舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.48,1:37:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.27,1:38:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把疲劳全部消掉哦
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.69,1:38:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.96,1:38:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疲劳好像都消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.73,1:38:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.54,1:39:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下去一点
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.88,1:39:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.52,1:40:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.64,1:40:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.17,1:41:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.58,1:41:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请使用我的肉穴来按摩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.87,1:42:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很紧哦
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.64,1:42:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面自己变紧了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.64,1:42:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又湿又紧哦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.26,1:43:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下流的汁液不停的流出来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.98,1:43:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下流的汁...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.05,1:43:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不停的流出去了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.97,1:44:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要摸摸看吗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.92,1:45:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉穴湿答答啰
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.46,1:45:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己看看
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.26,1:45:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要摸摸看吗
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.34,1:47:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来从后面来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.94,1:48:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把脚抬起来
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.75,1:48:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部在晃哦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.36,1:56:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.46,1:56:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.29,1:56:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.83,1:56:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下今晚我可以\N舒服的睡一觉了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.21,1:57:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我的按摩就值得了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.78,1:57:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以就这样和你一起睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.96,1:57:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得僵硬的时候\N随时可以叫我按摩哦
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.76,1:57:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起睡觉的话\N搞不好又会僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.60,1:57:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时我会再帮你按摩的
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.10,1:57:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点过来躺这边
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.29,1:57:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.11,1:58:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.47,1:58:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您今天指名\N由我为您服务
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.98,1:58:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会期待您下次的指名的
